frontMatter.code_usage:
The `ssnPattern` is available as a web-component pattern in the VA Forms library.

```jsx
import { ssnPattern } from '@department-of-veterans-affairs/platform-forms-system/patterns';
```

For screen reader accessibility, use the `formatNumberForScreenReader` utility:

```javascript
import { formatNumberForScreenReader } from '@department-of-veterans-affairs/platform-forms-system/utilities';

const formattedNumber = formatNumberForScreenReader(123456789);
```
